{"tid":1590183,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【10.1民陣遊行】十萬護旗手揮舞美國國旗，擁抱美帝嘅民主！自由！正義！","createTime":"2019-09-23T15:10:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T18:26:52.000Z","uid":167548,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"076be418c5c7be77b4ecd9205d63804301645cb9","tid":1590183,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:10:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2tCJyV8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2tCJyV8.jpg&h=4b6dd8de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q1n9uut.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ1n9uut.jpg&h=255f373a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n擁抱象徵民主、自由、正義嘅國旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中共反應最大是咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />是你地齊心奶美國旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />殖民香港20年支那未曾擁有嘅榮光<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NKS146e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNKS146e.jpg&h=83e11144&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n希望可以見到十萬支美國國旗佔領港島<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相信當日手足好撚想燒支那旗, 但是始終是犯法野(要包到實一實)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但是其他和理非, 我宣佈必須要有一支<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>美帝花旗</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n 一齊成為十萬旗手嘅一員<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申已買美國國旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />10.1港島見<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Fight For Freedom！<br />\nAmerica Stand with Hong Kong！ </span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"031c1708c4438807ebea7c96e9e79339c2231582","tid":1590183,"uid":167548,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:11:09.000Z","msg":"買左實體旗呢度留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c00ec847055ec3cd9613afce41a38a5f793a810d","tid":1590183,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:11:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589858</a>"},{"pid":"90516956401dfbb437cb257cd825ec3bece33f28","tid":1590183,"uid":167548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:11:33.000Z","msg":"拎旗仔呢度留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5191a3c1623afafa17abf17905ff12bb5fea8b27","tid":1590183,"uid":35831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:11:38.000Z","msg":"我係召集今日喺始創唱國歌嗰個小薯仔，我有啲嘢想講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590080\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590080</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6c50a2c0746e6181c3eaaf8ad2a1d6a247c549d1","tid":1590183,"uid":274149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:11:57.000Z","msg":"正吖！我愛我的國&mdash;&mdash;美國"},{"pid":"3dfe0015e46770818bb40e34569586784400f0a6","tid":1590183,"uid":167548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"031c1708c4438807ebea7c96e9e79339c2231582","tid":1590183,"uid":167548,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:11:09.000Z","msg":"買左實體旗呢度留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:12:04.000Z","msg":"Bought<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi